Remote PC Cast



Remote PC Cast

Version - 1.0

Remote PC Cast casts the host PC screen or specific element of PC screen to a web server and can be viewed or controlled from any other device!

Features



- Easy to use User friendly GUI interface.

- Cast every element of PC screen eg. software, games or the whole desktop

System Requriements



CPU - Intel Core i3 or higher

RAM - 6 GB or higher

HDD - 50MB of disk space required

Mouse and keyboard are required

Directx9.0c or higher is required

.Net Framework 4.5.2 or higher

Java Runtime Environment and Java Development Kit are required in case if software doesn't work.

Microsoft Visual C++ 2005 - 2019 is required

FAQ
 

1. Errors during installation of Remote PC Cast.
 
Answer 1
 
Make sure that you run 'RemotePCCast_setup.exe' as administrator when installing Remote PC Cast.

 

2. PC screen or element is not getting cast over web server or the servers are not getting created.

Answer 1

Make sure that the element or the window that is to be casted is visible and/or running in the background first before launching Remote PC Cast

Answer 2

It is highly recommended that you install Remote PC Cast in the directory where it does not require administrator rights  

eg: C:\
      Desktop
